Task::Lingua::Word2Num

Meta-package to install all PetaMem word-to-number conversion modules.
Part of the PetaMem Lingua number conversion suite.

INSTALLATION

    shell> cpanm Task::Lingua::Word2Num

    This installs all available Word2Num language modules.

    For all directions and all languages:

    shell> cpanm Task::Lingua::PetaMem

